						<summary>

						<p>Slab built into the fort wall.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1744, Chitrabhānu, Vaiśākha śu. 15,</hi> corresponding to 1822 A.D., May 6, Monday.</p>						

						<p>It records the construction of a fort by Madinā Sāni, wife of Havaldār Saidu Abdurasūla Mayā Sāhēb and the work was executed by Chaṁḍā Sāhēbu.</p>						

